1. Nationality:brazilian == Color:grey
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:rat
3. Nationality:french == Beverage:7up
4. Color:lilac is on the left of Color:black
5. Color:lilac == Beverage:juice
6. Cigar:montecristo == Pet:chinchilla
7. Color:turquise == Cigar:tiparillo
8. Beverage:almond-milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:nigerian is on the far left
10. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Pet:rabbit
11. Pet:frogs is on the left or right of Cigar:tiparillo
12. Cigar:apricotmaster == Beverage:soy-almond-milk
13. Nationality:mexican == Cigar:davidoff
14. Nationality:nigerian is on the left or right of Color:apricot
15. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Beverage:fanta

